extent: police say a bomber blew herself up outside a northern israel shopping center when she was stopped by a security guard
Sentence: israel has experienced its fifth suicide bombing in three days. police say a bomber blew herself up outside a northern israel shopping center when she was stopped by a security guard. three people plus the bomber were killed , and at least 30 others were hurt. the french press agency says the militant group " islamic jihad " is claiming responsibility .
